LatexCommand cite
key "ChaconRebollo2004,CastroDiaz2008"
literal "true"

\end_inset

 has been implemented and assessed too (called here E-well-balanced scheme).
 However this method has been found stable at first order only; thus it
 is not he employed scheme.
